# Elegant UI

Read `docs/architecture/ui-design-system.md` before building UI.

## Visual style

- Calm, spacious, professional — not flashy
- Neutral warm-gray base + **one** accent color
- `rounded-xl` cards, `shadow-sm` default, `shadow-md` on hover
- Geist Sans (or Inter fallback), 14–15px body

## Platform shell

- Shared top nav: Logo · Dashboard · Marketplace · Avatar
- Dashboard = subscribed apps only (small grid)
- Marketplace = search + category chips + **virtualized** grid for large catalogs

## Product cards

- 40px icon, name, 2-line description, single CTA (Launch / Subscribe)
- Badge for subscribed state
- Hover: subtle lift `translateY(-1px)` + border tint

## Marketplace (100+ products)

- Never render all products — use `@tanstack/react-virtual` + cursor pagination
- Debounced search (300ms), filters in URL (`?q=&category=`)
- Sticky search bar below nav
- Featured row (max 8) above main grid

## Loading & empty

- Skeleton placeholders — not spinners alone
- Empty states: one icon, one line, one button

## Do not

- Rainbow cards, heavy gradients, dense layouts
- Hardcoded product lists in components
- Different design systems on dashboard vs marketplace
